a. self only faction boost<br>
Increase Faction With Target<br>
b. can be purchased in Ak`Anon, Felwithe, Freeport, Neriak, Qeynos Casters Guilds, Erudin Palace Ench Guild<br>
<br>
Berserker Strength<br>
a. single target buff<br>
Increase Strength (20 - 25)<br>
Decrease Agility (-15)<br>
Absorb Damage (30 - 50)<br>
b. This spell does not stack well with other strength spells<br>
c. research only (see Research for components)<br>
<br>
Calm<br>
a. single target lull<br>
Lower Frenzy Radius to 5 Feet<br>
Lower React Radius to 5 Feet<br>
b. can be purchased in cleric, paladin, and casters guilds<br>
<br>
Cloud<br>
a. single target buff<br>
Increase AC (9 - 11)<br>
b. This spell does not stack with the Cleric or Shaman AC spells<br>
c. can be purchased in Ak`Anon, Felwithe, Freeport, Neriak, Qeynos Casters Guilds, Erudin Palace Ench Guild<br>
<br>
Color Shift<br>
a. point blank stun<br>
Personal Area: Stun All Targets (6 Secs)<br>
b. research only (see Research for components)<br>
<br>
Crystallize Mana<br>
a. single object enchantment<br>
Summon Object: Vial of Cloudy Mana<br>
b. requires a Poison Vial and a  Peridot<br>
c. can be purchased in Brownie Camp in Lesser Fay<br>
<br>
Endure Magic<br>
a. single target buff<br>
Increase Magic Resistance (20)<br>
b. this spell can be researched (see Research for components) or it can be purchased in cleric, shaman, druid, ranger, and casters guilds<br>
<br>
Feckless Might<br>
a. single target debuff<br>
Decrease Strength (26 - 30)<br>
b. It will not stack with other debuffs in the weaken series<br>
c. can be purchased in Ak`Anon, Felwithe, Freeport, Neriak, Qeynos Casters Guilds, Erudin Palace Ench Guild<br>
<br>
Illusion: Iksar<br>
a. self only illusion<br>
Change Form (Iksar)<br>
b. quest spell (see Quests for complete list)<br>
c. The spell is called &quot;Visions of Sebillite.&quot; <br>
<br>
Illusion: Ogre<br>
a. self only illusion and buff<br>
Change Form (Ogre)<br>
Faction Modifier (Ogre)<br>
New Combat Skill: Slam<br>
b. can be purchased in <br>
Ak`Anon, Felwithe, Freeport, Neriak, Qeynos Casters Guilds<br>
Erudin City Library<br>
Erudin Palace Ench Guild<br>
<br>
Illusion: Troll<br>
a. self only illusion and buff<br>
Change Form (Troll)<br>
Faction Modifier (Troll)<br>
New Combat Skill: Slam<br>
Increase Health Recovery (1 hp/tick)<br>
b. does not appear to stack with Skin Like Nature<br>
c. can be purchased in Ak`Anon, Felwithe, Freeport, Neriak, Qeynos Casters Guilds<br>
Erudin City Library<br>
Erudin Palace Ench Guild<br>
<br>
Shifting Sight<br>
a. self only vision alteration<br>
See through targets eyes<br>
Infravision<br>
b. can be purchased in Ak`Anon, Felwithe, Freeport, Neriak, Qeynos Casters Guilds, Erudin Palace Ench Guild<br>
<br>
Sisna`s Animation<br>
a. summon pet<br>
b. requires 3 tiny daggers<br>
c. can be purchased in Highhold Keep<br>
<br>
Sympathetic Aura<br>
a. single target buff<br>
Increase Charisma (16 - 18 ) <br>
b. can be purchased in Ak`Anon, Felwithe, Freeport, Neriak, Qeynos Casters Guilds, Erudin Palace Ench Guild<br>
<br>
Tashani<br>
a. single target debuff<br>
Decrease Magic Resistance (20 - 23)<br>
